// In environments with no Kubernetes cluster reachable (vanilla docker
// compose dev, fresh laptop, CI without a kind/k3d cluster), kubeconfig
// resolution returns an error rather than panicking — the binary continues
// without operators rather than crashing the whole process. NATS already
// degrades this way; this matches that pattern.
